WEBVTT

00:09:54.271 --> 00:10:00.372
The asylum seekers have been demonized
and then presented to the people.

00:10:00.372 --> 00:10:04.907
I hope my story and the story
of other Hazaras

00:10:04.907 --> 00:10:07.960
could shed some light to show the people

00:10:07.960 --> 00:10:12.261
how these people are suffering
in their countries of origin,

00:10:12.261 --> 00:10:16.180
and how they suffer,

00:10:16.180 --> 00:10:20.916
why they risk their lives to seek asylum.

00:10:20.916 --> 00:10:22.426
Thank you.

00:10:22.426 --> 00:10:23.665
(Applause)